<br>
a)  Working your way down from the sebilis zone in, 3 frogs are pulled, 2X jin Shammy, and a jin wizard, do you tash these mobs or is it a waste of time?<br>
<br>
b) you are down just on the far side of the zone out heading to disco, and have just come across the bridge, there are 4 mobs on your group and you manage to get them mezed, do you tash these as you are de-buffing them/slowing them or is it a waste of time?<br>
<br>
c) you get an over pull, loose your main damage dealer, and now have a warrior SK and wizard left, to dis assemble these mobs, do you tash or is it a waste of time?<br>
<br>
I would just kinda like to know, who tashs everything they fight or who thinks its a waste?<br>
<br>
